", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Water quality remains degraded due to... rain, high flow, little sunshine (and) temperatures below seasonal norms,\\\" it said.\", \"from\": 1035, \"to\": 1160, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Results posted online showed concentration of E. Coli was higher than the recommended limit in four locations of the river for practically all of the week of June 10 to 16.\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Seine is supposed to host both the Olympics opening ceremony as well as open-water events during the Games.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1340, \"end\": 1345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999772889894419, \"rank\": 2.2562543762072663e-05, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Paris has been holding its breath hoping for the river to be clean enough.\", \"from\": 1449, \"to\": 1527, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1453, \"end\": 1458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999569806741, \"rank\": 4.301940494857947e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In August 2023, the swimming marathon test events were cancelled because the water was too dirty, as were the swimming legs on two of the four days of triathlon and para-triathlon tests.\", \"from\": 1529, \"to\": 1715, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If the river is too polluted when the Olympics kick off, the plan B is to postpone open-water swimming events for a few days - not to move them to a new location.\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": []}, {\"se